pengu.messenger

Class PenguMessengerClient.ContactType

  • java.lang.Object
    • pengu.messenger.PenguMessengerClient.ContactType
  • Enclosing class:
    PenguMessengerClient

    public static class PenguMessengerClient.ContactType
extends java.lang.Object
    This class allows for Contact Type(Groups) Objects to be created so that they and their properties can be stored in an array with other Contact Types.
